-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span>"},{"pid":"19ee01b5b650c4c21a1f33a8f4f2e6d45ca1083f","tid":1347554,"uid":207462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:24:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搵文宣將警察黑社會政府扯上關係<br />\n統一戰線！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c5402c054b298fd74e14386044cf4120e79c5be9","tid":1347554,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:25:31.000Z","msg":"我信<br />\n擾亂視聽"},{"pid":"482aa90afb38c43bf6dbf329a4ce4adb00cfd832","tid":1347554,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:26:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a914e931e1933ace38839bdbf41822354ad12d28","tid":1347554,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:26:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span>"},{"pid":"528f1c75cc302a6d0a4110caf77f3417079b9a49","tid":1347554,"uid":195611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:29:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"32a60215872b9c4af766b7bc8039a5cd19ef690d","tid":1347554,"uid":7782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:29:25.000Z","msg":"好似睇緊十年第一幕咁......夾埋老黑做大龍鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658a59dd3bd95bd68d4e0af7cb4fe04f2750204d","tid":1347554,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:30:50.000Z","msg":"佢都戇鳩，佢依家用咩鎮壓？"},{"pid":"b2d923b43dbebf0ae0a784ab111c65a9fa7f5c17","tid":1347554,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:31:07.000Z","msg":"而家做好文宣，spread去外國媒體。template睇下面<br />\n<br />\n【一月、二月】 David R. Stilwell<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.state.gov/biographies/d